title: Eating Aliens (2012) (Pdf and Epub) Gooner
description:
Eating Aliens - One Man's Adventures Hunting Invasive Animal Species (2012) (Pdf & Epub) Gooner

Publisher: Storey Publishing, LLC (September 25, 2012)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 161212027X
ISBN-13: 978-1612120270

North America is under attack by a wide range of invasive animals. Black spiny-tailed iguanas in Florida, Asian carp in Missouri and Virginia, nutria in Louisiana, European green crabs in Connecticut, and other alien species throughout the United States are devouring our native plants and animals, pushing many to the brink of extinction. Jackson Landers has a unique solution to the problem: Eat them! This adventure narrative describes Landersâ€™s quest to hunt twelve invasive animal species and turn them into delicious meals, showing how anyone can feed a family while enjoying the thrill of the hunt and helping to protect and conserve the natural environment
